item.description: score:141 Chances: Tencent Music Entertainment Group has renewed its strategic licensing agreement with Universal Music Group, indicating a strong commitment to creating value for artists and music lovers. The company is a leading online music and audio entertainment platform in China, with a promising future in the music streaming industry.
